Describe

Looking for tough words? Don't want to open other apps to search meaning? Welcome to Describe - A Look Up Dictionary Ads free | Battery free ( 0% battery drain a day for searching around 50 words ) An interface between dictionaries and user. Copy Anywhere to view , synonyms and definition of the word It's work like "Look up" and "Define" application we often use on desktop. Describe provide multiple dictionaries to define selected word ( Wordnet, Livio, Google, Wikitionary ) Offline word definition using Livio dictionary ( Recommended for quick response ) Support for multiple language dictionary ( English, Italian, Spanish, French, German, Portuguese) Simple way to handle settings from notification panel. Multiple notification modes for different type of users Popup Notification: Instantly view definition of the word on copy. Silence Notification: Shown on notification panel on copying word clicking on notification to redirect for full definition screen. Floating Notification: On copying word a floating button will shown on screen, click on that to redirect for full definition screen.
